'''eXeAt eSports Club''' is an Argentinian team.

== Biography ==
'''eXeAt eSports Club''' is a professional multigaming organization located in Argentine. The organization was created on January 7, 2013, by Ra Jimenez, Pablo Svarsman and Diego Mendes Sakugawa. Formed their first League of Legends team in 2014.

